          "title": "Convergence in rounds",
          "desc": "Specialists AGREE or OBJECT. The design-auditor might challenge a vuln-analyst finding. Rounds continue until the panel aligns."
        },
        {
          "title": "Findings delivered.",
          "desc": "Filtered results in Markdown and console output. OWASP-mapped, severity-rated, with remediation guidance. Cost tracked."
        }
